title: Fed keeps interest rates steady
text:
Fed keeps interest rates steady 4:17am IST - 01:01 
The U.S. Federal Reserve kept interest rates unchanged, but said it anticipated inflation would rise this year, in a sign it is still on track to raise borrowing costs in March. Aleksandra Michalska reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
